    "Figure 4:4Figure 4: Constraint prompt structure Our approach to prompting the LLM begins by focusing on each input field.",
    "We employ a structured prompt, the details of which are outlined in Figure 4.",
    "This prompt includes the following information: (1) Time Context: This detail facilitates constraint generation for date and time fields by enabling the LLM to compare them with the current date.",
    "(2) Form Context: To provide general context about the form, we incorporate application's metadata (title and description) and labels from the form.",
    "This information informs the LLM about the type and purpose of the application and form, thereby facilitating more accurate and relevant constraint generation."
